            "data": "설정 완료\nJDBC URL   : jdbc:mysql://59.6.99.131:3306/QH_KSLAB?useSSL\u003dfalse\u0026allowPublicKeyRetrieval\u003dtrue\n저장 경로   : s3a://bigdata/kmon_new/parquet\n체크포인트  : s3a://bigdata/kmon_new/checkpoint/completed.txt\n"
